title: Astrobrights Punchy Pastel Assortment Cardstock, 8.5" x 11", 65 lb. 5-Color Assortment, 100 Sheets (91786)
description: Create fun and festive creations with this Astrobrights Punchy Pastel Assortment! These subtle colors complemented by a bright hue will be the perfect choice for any invitation, card-making, DIY crafting, and more! In this pack of 100 sheets, you will receive 20 sheets each of Lively Lemon, Breezy Blue, Bubble Gum, Merry Mint and Punchy Peach. Perfect for scrapbooking enthusiasts and crafters alike, the 8.5" x 11" cardstock is compatible with copiers, inkjet, and laser printers for striking and impressive prints. Plus, it’s lignin and acid-free so your creations won’t yellow over time. New colors, same great quality paper!
